Nilwm is a lightweight X window manager based on XCB.
It is inspired by following projects:
 - dwm
 - awesome
 - wmfs

FEATURES
 - Fast, small footprint.
 - 

COPYRIGHT
Nilwm is distributed under the GPL license.

DEBUG
$ Xephyr :1 -ac -br -noreset -screen 800x600 &
$ DISPLAY=:1
$ gdb nilwm-debug

or
$ xinit /path/to/nilwm -- :1
